.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
4 different games are played: snooker, chess, canasta, billiard
1. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person playing chess and the person who's hobby is writing##7
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Game   | chess      | snooker   | canasta | billiard  |

