3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is camping##7
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | 7up      | mirinda | sprite     |
| Hobby   | photography    | cooking | camping   | collecting |

