.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, grapefruit, orange, pepper
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, videographer, nurse, writer
1. the engineer is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the videographer##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far left or far right##3
4. the writer is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the person eating orange##7
5. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
6. the writer is on the left or right of the nurse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | pepper    | cherry   | grapefruit | orange  |
| Job   | engineer | nurse | writer    | videographer |

