.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, peas, strawberry, broccoli
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, horse, rabbit
1. the person eating peas is not the owner of the rabbit##6
2. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the person eating broccoli is the owner of the horse##1
4. the person eating strawberry is somewhere between the person eating broccoli and the person eating eggplant##7
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Food   | broccoli | strawberry | peas | eggplant |
| Pet           | horse   | rabbit    | dog       | hamster  |

