1. the engineer is not the bolivar-smoker##6
2. the scientist is on the right of the engineer##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the engineer##3
4. the engineer is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
5. the scientist is somewhere between the davidoff-smoker and the police-officer##7
6. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the swisher-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | security-guard | engineer | scientist | police-officer |
| Cigar   | davidoff         | swisher      | bolivar | siglo            |

