.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, october, september, july
4 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, rat, snake
1. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the owner of the snake##7
2. the person who's birthday is in october is not the owner of the rat##6
3. the owner of the mouse is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
4. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
5. the person who's birthday is in june is the owner of the dog##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | june | july | october | september |
| Pet           | dog    | mouse   | snake  | rat      |

