.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, blood-red, yellow, emerald
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, subway, trike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person who likes emerald is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the subway is the person who likes yellow##1
4. the person who likes yellow is not the person driving the bus##6
5. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person who likes yellow##7
7. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Color       | emerald | ebony | blood-red | yellow |
| Transport   | bike   | trike      | bus        | subway  |

