2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person who growsrose##5
5. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Flower         | tulip    | rose | begonia     | zinnia |
| Transport   | quad-bike | scooter  | motorbike | bus |

 